{"tid":1345784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向Law Society投訴何君堯條仆街","createTime":"2019-07-22T02:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T05:32:57.000Z","uid":168831,"like":143,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"a56906ac1de8a7048ad8f1a4edddf13ccd72358f","tid":1345784,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:47:46.000Z","msg":"我好肯定如果大家尋晚有睇直播、FB、TG，都唔會訓得好訓得着。白衫人要追究，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但背後個何君堯，一定要令佢仆街冚家產。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係一d法律界朋友向Law Society準備嘅投訴信，主要係講違反作為律師嘅專業措守，豪無道德可言，謹請Law Society調查。<br />\n<br />\n以下係投訴信template(<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得自己改下先send</span></span>):<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/file/d/1SXAYX-qtHRYe9OQbRs0ydFPNC5kOz8G7/edit?usp=docslist_api&amp;filetype=msword\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1SXAYX-qtHRYe9OQbRs0ydFPNC5kOz8G7%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Ddocslist_api%26filetype%3Dmsword&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=9c06d9b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/file/d/1SXAYX-qtHRYe9OQbRs0ydFPNC5kOz8G7/edit?usp=docslist_api&amp;filetype=msword</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋要填呢個投訴表格(係，係好撚煩，但要搞條仆街煩都要做):<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=15SsVwon8c2gLYHvSYVxmxpKiSR1IjHHI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D15SsVwon8c2gLYHvSYVxmxpKiSR1IjHHI&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqcyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=bb08a598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=15SsVwon8c2gLYHvSYVxmxpKiSR1IjHHI</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係指引:<br />\n<br />\nLaw Soc requires complainants to fill in their name and title (p 1 of the PDF), sign and date the form (p 5 of the PDF), and also fill in a personal data form (p. 7-8 of the PDF) <br />\nThen email to complaints@hklawsoc.org.hk <br />\n<br />\nComplainants need not be solicitors!!! General public can fill in and complain as well. Do circulate this!"},{"pid":"515e921d0546a6063e9fc286d0db59c0c341c03b","tid":1345784,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"!"},{"pid":"f28373161470dbbaf1cadfd54245bcd110e44823","tid":1345784,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe507d22be8c8ea4edb85c66194de30e841851ab","tid":1345784,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非、文宣，全部同我入黎填左佢!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"7b1af31e43898b4674079bf1fa394f504491e0d3","tid":1345784,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:51:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑結集 縱容恐襲</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1e60bdfd94f89cf709011bc78ff9fd861c74a1c0","tid":1345784,"uid":212706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:51:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c12bcbc72b69007a44b173d58b191cd8bdfdfbef","tid":1345784,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:55:12.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係推，推完要做野！"},{"pid":"6c26b79100494921bdcd72646a919a539c04a174","tid":1345784,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f395633c80195927b848a2cff915b820895449e","tid":1345784,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d17ec8b71b69683c71ccde3b4e73b5207b9be561","tid":1345784,"uid":73444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"係咪要print 出黎寄, 定係send email? 我唔怕煩, 最緊要有用!!!"},{"pid":"9a8b8f66ca0ea34ff769af2fd56505c573944160","tid":1345784,"uid":168831,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d17ec8b71b69683c71ccde3b4e73b5207b9be561","tid":134