"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4d3e922711c53d44c2ca7402559af463378932","tid":1345784,"uid":255510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4bb79d37f2546372f23d18c121c9ca77ba8ba95c","tid":1345784,"uid":286470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:18:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348154/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348154/page/1</a><br />\n修訂咗，跟返update咗嘅Professional Code<br />\n唔怕麻煩嘅自己改<br />\n<br />\nPrinciples<br />\n<br />\n8. The criminal, indiscriminate violence employed by the gang of men in white shirts in Yuen Long was shocking to any right-thinking member of the public. One would have thought that it should be unthinkable for any self-respecting person to be associated with such a criminal gang or any member thereof. Mr. Ho not only proves this wrong, he appears to be publicly commending members of the gang for their actions on the night of 21st-22nd July 2019. <br />\n<br />\n9. It is provided in Principle 1.03 of the Hong Kong Solicitors&rsquo; Guide to Professional Conduct that &ldquo;a solicitor is an officer of the Court (see s 3(2) of the Legal Practitioners Ordinance (Cap. 159), and should conduct himself appropriately in professional and private matters&rdquo;. As per Ma CJHC (as he then was) in A Solicitor v The Law Society of Hong Kong (unreported) CACV 107/2005, 7th July 2006 at paragraph 79: &ldquo;A solicitor is a member of an honourable profession, an officer of the court and one of the three bodies (together with the courts and barristers) primarily responsible for the administration of justice. The public&rsquo;s perception of a solicitor is exactly these terms.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n10. I take the view that a) Mr. Ho&rsquo;s conduct is unbefitting of a solicitor, and b) contrary to principle 1.03 of the Guide and/or Rule 2 of the Solicitors&rsquo; Practice Rules (Cap. 159H) in that Mr. Ho did not conduct himself appropriately but conducted himself in a manner likely to bring the profession into disrepute. <br />\n<br />\n11. As a person with a public profile (including being a former President of the Law Society), Mr. Ho is well known to be a solicitor. Mr. Ho&rsquo;s acts in the public eye would and do in fact affect the public perception of solicitors. <br />\n<br />\n12. Moreover, the charge of conduct unbefitting of a solicitor is not limited to acts performed in the capacity of a solicitor (Halsbury&rsquo;s Laws of Hong Kong [240.081], A Solicitor v The Law Society of Hong Kong (unreported) CACV 107/2005, 7th July 2006 at paragraph 82). Similarly, Principle 1.03 of the Guide explicitly states that a solicitor is to conduct himself.&rdquo; (emphasis added). The Commentary to Principle 1.03 continues: &ldquo;As an Officer of the Court, proper standards of behaviour whether in his practice or in his independent business activities are required of a solicitor as a member of an honourable profession.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n13. I find the conduct of Mr. Ho abhorrent and a disgrace to the profession, and hence ask that the Law Society do take prompt disciplinary action accordingly. I look forward to hearing from the Law Society in relation to progress in this case."},{"pid":"760a148d5604a94f3645e3328dcc2adc425e497b","tid":1345784,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"a013013f4813c8fda9f3ff26b6aa457a30af82c8","tid":1345784,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:26:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64dfeb503d293695d23f4649a458064a2c4cb1ea","tid":1345784,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b338cad5301b4a3c406cab5283f5a5c60133cb5","tid":1345784,"uid":168831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:44:45.000Z","msg":"推呀屌你何君堯"}]}